== Configurar SSH

Ainda como root

nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config

Porta 65522
LoginGraceTime 30
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
MaxAuthTries 3
X11Forwarding no
DenyUsers root
AllowUsers ribafs

sudo service ssh restart

== Sincronizar a chave do ssh do desktop para o servidor

apt install rsync

rsync --archive --chown=ribafs:ribafs ~/.ssh /home/ribafs

Conectar com ribafs

exit

lin

cd ~/

nano .bashrc

Colar
alias cw='clear;cd /var/www/html;ls'
alias aptes='apachectl configtest'
alias apres='sudo service apache2 restart'
alias aprel='sudo service apache2 reload'
alias mrel='sudo service mysql reload'
alias mres='sudo service mysql restart'

Salvar e fechar
source .bashrc



